# ⚡ Voltix Video Player (Advanced Engine)

A modern, full-featured media player built with Python and PyQt6. 

Voltix Advanced features a sleek, borderless-style dark UI redesign (Catppuccin Mocha-inspired palette), persistent local database storage, drag-and-drop mechanics, and deep media playback controls.

---

## 🎬 Features

### 💎 New & Advanced Core Features
- **Modern Dark UI Redesign:** Re-engineered using a premium dark-mode theme, optimized layouts, and a dedicated sidebar layout.
- **Media Library & Playlist Panel:** Powered by an integrated local database (`voltix_library.db`) to persistently save your custom playlists and track playback history across active sessions.
- **Drag & Drop Engine:** Drop any compatible media file directly onto the window viewport to instantly start playback.
- **Large Center Play Button Overlay:** An intuitive center-screen button that dynamically overlays the video, allowing you to click anywhere on the video viewport to toggle playback.
- **Subtitle Loader Engine (.srt):** Clean, custom overlay for synchronized subtitles. Automatically searches for a matching `.srt` file in the same directory as the playing media file, or lets you load one manually.
- **Playback Speed Control:** Dynamic hardware rate scaling dropdown supporting playback speeds from `0.5x` up to `2.0x`.
- **Open-With-Voltix Integration Support:** Natively parses command-line file path payloads (`sys.argv`), enabling you to set Voltix as your operating system's default media player.
- **EXE-Safe Resource Routing:** Hardened virtual file mapping utilizing absolute path calculations to ensure assets like `logo.ico` load flawlessly when compiled with PyInstaller.

### 🎥 Supported Media Codecs
- **Video:** MP4, MKV, AVI, MOV, WMV, WEBM
- **Audio:** MP3, WAV, FLAC, OGG, AAC, M4A

### ⚙ Player Controls
- Modernized Play / Pause / Stop mechanics
- Persistent Volume Slider
- Smooth Video Timeline Seeking
- Dynamic Frame Layout Time Display (`HH:MM:SS`)
- Seamless Fullscreen Toggle (`F11` or Keybind)

### ⌨ Keyboard Shortcuts (Configurable)
| Default Key | Action | Description |
|:---:|---|---|
| **Space** | Play / Pause | Toggle media playback state |
| **O** | Open File | Open system file dialog explorer |
| **F** / **F11** | Fullscreen | Toggle video fullscreen viewport display |
| **S** | Settings | Launch advanced configuration pane |
